                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900526-41-off189 t17900526-41-cd190"></join>, one woollen cloak, value 3 s. two muslin caps, value 4 s. one child's cap, value 2 s. 6 d. two childs lawn caps, value 3 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17900526-41-victim431" type="victimName">
                     Benjamin 
                     Powers
                  <interp inst="t17900526-41-victim431" type="surname" value="Powers"></interp>
